                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Charlotte Schultze</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Now from there on we don&#39;t know anything more. At any rate the Gestapo brought us his things, and asserted that he had shot himself.</p>
